{
  "stem": "17426.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although I was quite younger-- I was five years younger than my brother and three years younger than my sister-- I always felt because I grew up among those older two brother and sister, I felt that I'm as grown up as they are.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They treated me that way, and that's how I felt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when it came to certain activities where at 19-year-old one could take part in, partake, and I could not as a 14-year-old one, I was very unhappy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I nudged and nudged till they took me along.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was kind of introduced to a more mature life than I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I appreciate that very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very often my brother would not take me along, and my sister would.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that is whether they had gone to another town for a organizational meeting or went just as friends to visit friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was sort of like the fifth wheel, if you will.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We also [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] participated in a dramatic circle, which was produced-- which the plays in Dobra.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And oftentimes, we went out of Dobra with the play, and I was always part of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even so that I was 14 years old, I sometime played a 20-year-old young man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They dressed me up in a long suit, put me on a chair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there I was, performing for, for I said a 20-year-old man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of them that I remember is [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The other one is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were two others, in which I had a very prominent role.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do not remember the name anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it-- it went something like-- it was a rich Jewish assimilated family with a daughter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was the butler to the man of the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
